summary:
A scientist with people skills that combines creative thinking and logical reasoning to realize the customer's dream. I've worked on a broad range of projects within the radiology, neurology and cardiology domain, ranging from low-level implementation to high-level requirements, from 3D visualization (MR, CT) in a post-processing workstation to workflow analysis in a PACS environment, while never compromising the needs of the customer.

Specialties: - Eliciting requirements
- Translating customer requirements into a prototype
- Generating intellectual property
- High-performance 3D visualization
- Computer science
